transcripts: When I found out I got nominated I couldn't believe it you know, it's it's crazy that my record would be worthy for an R&B nomination. I freaked out for a little bit, and then I did a little happy dance, give them a little bit of this, gonna give them a swang, gonna do that thing, hmm hmm hmm, yeah you know a little bit of that.
